OL,3,CCancer patient thanks clinical trial
OL,4,Cfor years lived since terminal
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FTerry Berry spoke to ITV correspondent
OL,8,FRob Smith about how a bout of food
OL,9,Fpoisoning led to a cancer diagnosis.
OL,11,FA cancer patient says he has clinical
OL,12,Ftrials to thank for surviving years
OL,13,Fsince being told he had months to live.
OL,15,FTerry Berry, from Wigan, was diagnosed
OL,16,Fwith terminal bile duct cancer in 2020
OL,17,Fand warned he may have just six to 12
OL,18,Fmonths left.
