OL,3,CCancer patient thanks clinical trial
OL,4,Cfor years lived since terminal
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FMedics offered Terry two different
OL,8,Fclinical trials, at The Christie in
OL,9,FManchester, including one for a drug
OL,10,Ftargeted at an enzyme alteration in
OL,11,Fhis tumour cells.
OL,13,FHe now credits those trials with
OL,14,Fallowing him to see major milestones
OL,15,Fover the past four years.
OL,17,F"My daughter's wedding. My fourth
OL,18,Fgrandchild being born. Everything
OL,19,Freally.
OL,21,F"Just getting up every day."
