OL,3,CCancer patient thanks clinical trial
OL,4,Cfor years lived since terminal
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FAsked what it is like to play with the
OL,8,Fgrandson he never expected to meet, he
OL,9,Fsaid: "Brilliant. Absolutely
OL,10,Fbrilliant."
OL,12,FThe drug treatment Terry now takes
OL,13,Fevery day, Ivosidenib, is not a cure
OL,14,Fbut holds his cancer in-check.
OL,16,FIt helps patients where bile duct
OL,17,Fcancer has spread elsewhere in the
OL,18,Fbody and whose tumours have an
OL,19,Falteration to an enzyme called IDH1.
