OL,3,CCancer patient thanks clinical trial
OL,4,Cfor years lived since terminal
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FOncologist Dr Mairead McNamara said:
OL,8,F"For years, chemotherapy was the
OL,9,Fstandard option for treatment but
OL,10,FIvosidenib has become available and
OL,11,Fit's approved now by the NHS.
OL,13,F"They're not available for all because
OL,14,Fnot all patients have these
OL,15,Falterations. But for those where it is
OL,16,Fa possibility, it offers a great
OL,17,Fadditional option."
